title: Witold Czarnecki
text: Witold Wojciech Czarnecki (born 12 April 1953 in <a href="Murowana%20Go%C5%9Blina">Murowana Goślina</a>) is a Polish politician. He was elected to the <a href="Sejm">Sejm</a> on 25 September 2005, getting 12,826 votes in 36 <a href="Kalisz">Kalisz</a> district as a candidate from the <a href="Law%20and%20Justice">Law and Justice</a> list.
